    "Additionally, there is a need to develop more robust and accurate methods for relation extraction and classification.Finally, the KG-augmented LLMs approach is initially implemented by using off-the-shelf tools from Neo4J.",
    "The KG-retrieval engine extracts triplets.",
    "The advantages of this method are that the information is condensed and accurate, and the triplets also represent relations to help the LLM answer questions better.",
    "However, the triplets retrieval engine only extracts relevant triples and does not have a ranking mechanism to help eliminate redundant triples.",
    "In this article, we introduce an approach to open intent discovery using unsupervised learning methods."
